Download and Enjoy Bleach Logon Screen




Bring the fantastic anime Bleach to your login and logoff screen. With Ichigo, Rukia and all Shinigamis are in your computer desktop to fight against the hollows. Bleach Logon Screen contain 5 high quality backgrounds to replace the default Windows Logon Wallpaper.


